        <div class="entry-content">
            <p>ITM College commenced its education and training business in 1986 and has globally trained over 6.4 million students. ITM College is an ISO 9001:2000 organization and the first IT Training and Education company to get this certification for Education Support Services in 1993.</p>
            <p>ITM College has presence in more than 40+ emerging countries through its two main streams of businesses – Individual training and Enterprise Business. As a leader in career education, it has over 1305 centres of learning across the world.</p>
            <p>Under Individual Training, ITM College offers career and professional training through its ITM College Computer Education, Arena Animation & Maya Academy of Advanced Cinematics (both in Animation & Multimedia), ITM College Hardware & Networking Academy, ITM College Aviation & Hospitality Academy and ITM College English Learning Academy brands.</p>
            <p>Enterprise business includes Content Development (ITM College Learning Services), Training and Assessment Solutions for Corporates & Institutions (ITM College Training Solutions, ITM College Assessment & Testing Solutions).</p>
